headline: Is Now the Right Time to Revisit Netflix After Yankees Streaming Deal?
summary: If you have Netflix stock on your mind, you are not alone. With a last close of $1,210.61 and a jaw-dropping 71.1% return over the past year, Netflix has been a headline-maker for all the right reasons. Year-to-date, shares are up 36.5%, but recent action has been a bit more subdued, dipping 1.3% in the past week and treading water with a 0.2% gain across the last month. This move comes as Netflix flexes its muscle in new ways, like landing its first exclusive MLB stream for the Yankees’...
